title: Grateful Dead Live at Indiana Convention Center on 1979-12-07
description: Minglewood Blues, Tennessee Jed, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Don't Ease Me In-> El Paso, Big Railroad Blues, Easy To Love You-> It's All Over Now, Althea, The Music Never Stopped China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Eyes Of The World-> Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> Wharf Rat-> Around & Around-> Johnny B. Goode, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: SBD I put out a really nice sbd of this show back in april. I don't know why it isn't up here yet. This is a pretty average show, except for a great jam before drums...cm
